    <paragraphs>
      <title>Office Hours</title>
      <p>
        My office is located in SW-341, but I will host office hours from 3:30p-5:30p and will be held in the MPLC (see next section). I am also available for appointment if these times do not work for you. Office hours are a great place to get help on homework, ask questions about course materials, or even just have a cup of coffee and chat. They will be your single greatest resource outside of class, so please use them!
      </p>
